{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Create AI and Conquer the Dungeon.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Algolemeth is a dungeon RPG where you send golems equipped with program into a dungeon for fully automated exploration. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Challenge the Dungeon through Trial and Error!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2731030/extras/battle_en_small.gif?t=1738938870\" />As an alchemist, players create autonomously operating golems, forming parties to undertake automatic dungeon conquests. Once the golems are dispatched into the dungeon, all you can do is watch. Analyze enemy actions, iterate through trial and error, and aim to conquer the dungeon!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Bring Back Parts and Strengthen Your Golems!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2731030/extras/modulerack_en_small.gif?t=1738938870\" />Various enhancement parts can be found in the dungeon. Among them are those that directly increase the golem's physical abilities and modules that allow for new action logic. Create your own unique golems with the parts you acquire!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Not Just Battle, But Fully Automated Exploration!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2731030/extras/explorer_en_small.gif?t=1738938870\" />Players can control exploration actions in the dungeon using exploration AI. Decide who will unlock the treasure chest, whether to continue exploring based on current health status, or whether to retreat. The actions of your party are dependent on the AI you've created.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2731030?t=1738938870","background_raw":"https://shared.akam